<blockquote class="aesop-component-align-left" style="font-size: 1em;">“My art crew started to pick up and I started being able to do that as a paid career. I didn't want to abandon the other work that I did, so I experimented with different ways that I could combine the two,”</blockquote>
</div>
Although he works with people from all ages, children are often more willing to get involved with the creation of Bergner’s work.
<div id="aesop-image-component-814-4" class="aesop-component aesop-image-component ">
<div class="aesop-content">
