<audio id="audio-814-5" class="wp-audio-shortcode" style="width: 100%; visibility: hidden;" preload="none" controls="controls"><source type="audio/mpeg" src="http://www.dandavies23.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5-Doing-something-that-you-actually-enjoy.mp3?_=5" /><a href="http://www.dandavies23.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5-Doing-something-that-you-actually-enjoy.mp3">http://www.dandavies23.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5-Doing-something-that-you-actually-enjoy.mp3</a></audio></aside>
<div id="aesop-quote-component-814-7" class="aesop-component aesop-quote-component aesop-component-align-left aesop-quote-type-pull quote-is-parallax quote-left-right " style="color: #ffffff; height: auto; width: 100%;">
<blockquote class="aesop-component-align-left" style="font-size: 1em;">“I don't think of this as charity, because it's not something that I'm doing, just to help other people. I LOVE what I do, I love helping but I also love it for selfish reasons and that's the best way to contribute. Do something that helps others and you love... and really you're going to be so much better at doing something so much more useful, if you do something that you enjoy.”</blockquote>
</div>
